<span class="ph">질의</span>: <span class="ps">"지난 1시간 동안 ewas 서버에서 CPU가 90% 넘은 구간 보여줘"</span></div>
      </div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot dot-req">2</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
      <div class="step-body"><div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-head">
          <span class="sc sc-llm">LLM PLUGIN</span>
          <span class="step-action">Ollama에 PromQL 변환 요청</span>
          <span class="dir dir-req">→ POST /v1/chat/completions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="payload"><span class="pc">POST</span> http://ollama-server:<span class="ph">11434</span>/v1/chat/completions
{
  <span class="pk">"model"</span>   : <span class="ps">"qwen2.5-coder:14b"</span>,
  <span class="pk">"messages"</span>: [
    { <span class="pk">"role"</span>: <span class="ps">"system"</span>, <span class="pk">"content"</span>: <span class="ps">"당신은 Prometheus PromQL 전문가입니다. 자연어를 PromQL로 변환하세요."</span> },
    { <span class="pk">"role"</span>: <span class="ps">"user"</span>,   <span class="pk">"content"</span>: <span class="ps">"지난 1시간 동안 ewas 서버에서 CPU가 90% 넘은 구간"</span> }
  ]
}</div>
      </div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot dot-resp">3</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
      <div class="step-body"><div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-head">
          <span class="sc sc-ollama">OLLAMA</span>
