  }
}</div>
      </div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot dot-act">6</div></div>
      <div class="step-body"><div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-head">
          <span class="sc sc-grafana">GRAFANA</span>
          <span class="step-action">결과 시각화 완료 — 패널 렌더링</span>
          <span class="dir dir-done">✓ 완료</span>
        </div>
        <div class="payload"><span class="po">✓</span> 시계열 그래프 렌더링 완료
<span class="po">✓</span> CPU 90% 초과 구간: 14:02 ~ 14:08  (<span class="pw">91~93%</span>)
